(Did my post with Cheetor scratching Magmatron go through?)


Terrorsaur:




Terrorsaur transformed to his beast mode and flew up to thick mound of 
stalactite in the cave. He perched ontop of it like a roosting bird, and 
looked at the things below him. He thought it was a perfect personal spot. 
It wasn't out of sight, but he liked it. It gave him that superiority in 
height. He ducked his head under his wing and closed his eyes.
